      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 125,
      "width": 351,
      "height": 203,
      "text": "x% of y = (x/100) × y\nWhat % is X of Y = (X/Y) × 100\n\n% Increase = [(New-Old)/Old] × 100\n% Decrease = [(Old-New)/Old] × 100\n\nNew Value = Old × (1 ± %/100)\n\nWHY: \"Percent\" = per-hundred. We scale any\nfraction to a base of 100 for comparison.\n\nEx: 20% of 350 = (20/100)×350 = 70\n    What % is 42 of 168? = (42/168)×100 = 25%",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 500,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 5,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f0"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "x% of y = (x/100) × y\nWhat % is X of Y = (X/Y) × 100\n\n% Increase = [(New-Old)/Old] × 100\n% Decrease = [(Old-New)/Old] × 100\n\nNew Value = Old × (1 ± %/100)\n\nWHY: \"Percent\" = per-hundred. We scale any\nfraction to a base of 100 for comparison.\n\nEx: 20% of 350 = (20/100)×350 = 70\n    What % is 42 of 168? = (42/168)×100 = 25%",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_6",
