    {
      "id": "el_31",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 813,
      "width": 231,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Formula = (X/Y) x 100\nStep 2: = (45/180) x 100 = 25%\n\n  |████████░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░|\n  |◄─ 45 ─►|◄──── 135 ────────►|\n     25%           75%\n\nTRICK:\n45/180 = 1/4 → know 1/4 = 25%\n\nAnswer: 25% ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
