      "groupIds": [
        "type_2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Formula = (X/Y) x 100\nStep 2: = (45/180) x 100 = 25%\n\n  |████████░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░|\n  |◄─ 45 ─►|◄──── 135 ────────►|\n     25%           75%\n\nTRICK:\n45/180 = 1/4 → know 1/4 = 25%\n\nAnswer: 25% ✓",
