    {
      "id": "el_46",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1168,
      "width": 353,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Year-by-year:\n  Yr 0: 50000\n  Yr 1: 55000 (x1.1)\n  Yr 2: 60500 (x1.1)\n  Yr 3: 66550 (x1.1)\n\n  50000 ─x1.1─→ 55000 ─x1.1─→ 60500 ─x1.1─→ 66550\n\nTRICK:\nFormula: P = P0 x (1 + r/100)^n\n= 50000 x (1.1)^3 = 50000 x 1.331\n= 66550\n\nAnswer: 66550 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 4600,
