      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Year-by-year:\n  Yr 0: 50000\n  Yr 1: 55000 (x1.1)\n  Yr 2: 60500 (x1.1)\n  Yr 3: 66550 (x1.1)\n\n  50000 ─x1.1─→ 55000 ─x1.1─→ 60500 ─x1.1─→ 66550\n\nTRICK:\nFormula: P = P0 x (1 + r/100)^n\n= 50000 x (1.1)^3 = 50000 x 1.331\n= 66550\n\nAnswer: 66550 ✓",
