    {
      "id": "el_66",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1550,
      "width": 281,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Let B=100, A=120 (20% more)\nStep 2: Diff=20, Base=A=120\nStep 3: B less by (20/120)x100 = 16.67%\n\n  B |████████████|  100\n  A |██████████████| 120 (+20%)\n  A→B: 20/120 = 16.67% less\n\nTRICK:\nFormula: x/(100+x) x 100%\n= 20/120 x 100 = 16.67%\nPairs: +10%→-9.09%, +25%→-20%\n\nAnswer: B is 16.67% less than A ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
