      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_12"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 37.5% of 480\nStep 2: = (37.5/100) x 480\n        = 0.375 x 480 = 180\n\n  37.5% = 3/8\n  480 ──×3/8──→ 180\n\nTRICK:\n37.5% = 3/8, so (3/8) x 480 = 180\nCOMMUTATIVE: x% of y = y% of x\n8% of 25 = 25% of 8 = 2\n\nAnswer: 180 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
